Just went on my 3rd and 4th LDON last night, these were in Miragul's and I had a great time.  Group was Paladin, Warrior, Ranger, Cleric, Druid and me.  I was in charge of slow/snare, CC and hasting the group, and of course manasong.
<br />

<br />
On to my noob question(s):
<br />

<br />
What do I do with the charm slot?  I see that I can purchase charms from the LDON merchants, which I understand only work in LDON.  So, do I purchase one of these and then put the adventurer's stone in it?  It seems like I am missing something leaving the charm slot empty.
<br />

<br />
OR... am I totally off base and need to read somewhere else on this?
<br />

<br />
Thanks for the assistance.
<br />

<br />
Bedji
