				<td class="PanelBodyAlternate"><span class="SmallBoldText">Re: LDON, Charm Slot and the Adventurer's Stone<a name="15358"/></span><br><span class="SmallText"> Posted: </span><span class="SmallText">Jan 13 04 1:13 AM</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span>Your augment gainst HP and Mana for every ten successful missions completed at each theme (zone) and I hear it really gets good when you have 10 at each.  You hail the npc that does nothing else (not a merchant etc.) at each camp after every second win, and it will tell you you have gained important or valuable information, if you ony have one of the two needed to talk to him he says you need more adventures or something.
<br />

<br />
The augment upgrading is independent of your charm upgrade, so if you have a PoP figurine, it goes up also with additional flags.
<br />

<br />
Hope that helps,
<br />

<br />
Sinfonian</span></td>
