				<td colspan="2"><span>One other thing to note.  If you don't have it on your intricate figurine, but on some random adv point bought charm, you can always use a solvent to take it off when you do get your figurine.  Just hail any of the adventurers at the wayfarer camps that give you an adventure stone after you lost yours to the solvent, and hail them.  They will automatically give you a new one and based on its power, it will come back with the same stats on it.  I used to have mine on an adv bought charm, but now it's on the figurine.  I need more PoP flags though hehe.  You don't need 10 to each LDoN area btw, you can get it from one place.  I have 50 wins in Mistmoore, 20 in Takish, and 10 in Miragul, and my is just like everyone else.</span></td>
