				<td colspan="2"><span>Well Maka, this comes from Casters Realm...
<br />
Type 1 - Single stat enhancements  (self explaining)
<br />
Type 2 - Multiple stat enhancements (also self explaining)
<br />
Type 3 - Worn Effects (such as haste, regeneration, etc.)
<br />
Type 4 - Weapon Procs
<br />
Type 5 - Single Weapon Damage additions (single changes to a weapon's damage I am thinking from what they said)
<br />
Type 6 - Multiple Weapon Damage additions (same as 5, but giving multiple types of damage, perhaps affecting delay as well?)
<br />
Type 7 - Here's The one that I don't know... and i've been looking everywhere, but can't find it. sorry
<br />
Type 8 - Plane of Time Items Only (well, it's augments for plane of time items only...)
<br />

<br />
Hoped this helped... also, if anyone discovers/knows what type 7 is, it would be a great help to get the information.
<br />
                                                      Budian</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
				<td colspan="2"><span class="SmallText"><hr size="1" align="left" width="15%">Budian Songheart, Stromm</span></td>
			</tr><tr>
