				<td colspan="2"><span>Just an FYI..when you complete a adventure camp and hail the NPCs you will know that that portion is done when the last hailed NPC says,&quot; You know more about these creatures than I do. Perhaps you can teach me a thing or two.&quot;
<br />

<br />
I believe it is 72 wins in a EF and SRO addys and 78 in the other camps ( NRO, BB, EC).
<br />

<br />
I currently have all camps maxxed cept SRO and and my addy stone is at +9 on all stats, saves and ac and +81hp and mana.
<br />

<br />
A maxxed stone is +10 in all and +100 hp and mana.
<br />

